# Deep Analysis — {{ profile.metadata.name }}

This rule provides structured prompts for Cursor-assisted deep analysis.
Run all steps in sequence. **For each finding, cite the file path that proves it.**

Write ALL findings to a single file: **`deep-analysis.yaml`** in the repo root.

After completing all steps, run:
```
product-builders ingest-deep --name {{ profile.metadata.name }} --repo .
```

